sequenceDiagram
  participant User as User Python
  participant RclpyPy as rclpy pure Python
  participant Meta as DemoStatus metaclass
  participant DemoExt as demo_pkg_s__rosidl_typesupport_c.so
  participant RclpyExt as _rclpy_pybind11.so
  participant GenPy as libdemo_pkg__rosidl_generator_py.so
  participant Rcl as rcl / rmw

  User->>RclpyPy: create_publisher(DemoStatus, topic)
  RclpyPy->>Meta: check_for_type_support
  alt capsules not loaded
    Meta->>DemoExt: import_type_support demo_pkg
    DemoExt-->>Meta: five PyCapsules on module
    Meta-->>Meta: store on __class__
  end
  RclpyPy->>RclpyExt: Publisher(node_handle, DemoStatus, topic, qos)
  Note over RclpyExt,Rcl: rcl_publisher_init → store shared_ptr rcl_publisher_t
  RclpyExt-->>RclpyPy: _rclpy.Publisher object
  RclpyPy->>RclpyPy: Publisher(impl, msg_type, ...) + node._publishers.append

  User->>RclpyPy: publish(msg instance)
  RclpyPy->>RclpyExt: publish(msg)
  Note over RclpyExt,Meta: rclpy binding reads msg.__class__ capsules
  RclpyExt->>GenPy: convert_from_py via _CONVERT_FROM_PY capsule
  RclpyExt->>Rcl: rcl_publish + _TYPE_SUPPORT capsule
